data.description: It's a beautiful day @ 1414 Millbro Cir.  You must come tour this freshly remodeled renovated move in ready home.  The house offers 4 bedrooms, master and 1 bedroom on the main, 3 full bathrooms, sun room, bonus area plus bonus room.  Two driveways and one car detached garage with additional storage.  The kitchen looks amazing with new butcher block countertops, updated fixtures, and stainless steel appliance package.  SO MUCH SPACE with 2,500+ on a 1/4 acre lot.  4 entrances on each side of the house, two to the top main level and 2 to the lower level.  Covered front porch and back patio.  New roof was put on Q4 2020. Come take a tour today.  If you fall in love this house could be your new home next month in June 2021. Seller will provide a $420 Choice 1 Year Home Warranty & $3,000 window allowance via credit at closing, if requested on the offer.  Please View 360 Virtual Tour.
